name: differences / frictions ii
description:
We are children of the difference. Differences mean frictions. We need to acknowledge them, and learn to live with them. No friction = no joy. Read more at iillucid.com/wachet-auf-ruft-uns-die-stimme/

Artwork by Marcelo Soria-Rodríguez @msoriaro.

Made with Processing, 6000x6000 px.
